Download PostgreSQL to your Mac from 
https://www.postgresql.org/download/


Then go php.ini file and remove the “;” in front of each:

php.ini file location : Application/xampp/etc/php.ini

;extension=pdo_pgsql
;extension=pgsql


# Using POSTGRES in Laravel

DB_CONNECTION=pgsql
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=5432
DB_DATABASE=database_name
DB_USERNAME=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=your_choosen_password

